# 📊 Customer Churn Prediction

## 📌 Overview
The **Customer Churn Prediction** project leverages **data analysis and machine learning** to identify customers at risk of leaving a service.  
By predicting churn, businesses can take **proactive actions** to retain customers and improve customer satisfaction.  

## 🔍 Dataset Information
- **Source**: Customer data obtained from [Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/)  
- **Size**: 10,000 records  
- **Key Features**:
  - `CustomerID`: Unique customer identifier  
  - `Tenure`: Duration of customer retention  
  - `MonthlyCharges`: Monthly subscription fee  
  - `TotalCharges`: Total amount charged  
  - `Churn`: Did the customer leave? (1 = Yes, 0 = No)  

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **Programming Language**: Python 🐍  
- **Libraries**:
  - Pandas, NumPy (Data Analysis)  
  - Matplotlib, Seaborn (Data Visualization)  
  - Scikit-learn (Machine Learning)  
  - XGBoost, LightGBM (Advanced Models)  

